name: Summer BB - Fate Grand Order
description:
"A~loha~! Now then, our vacation starts here!"

Tag: summer bb, fgo

Like always, I cannot guarantee you'll get amazing results, but hopefully you'll find the model worth your time.

Trained in: NAI

Sample images are all Kotos.

Best weight to use is around: 0.7-1. Stage 1 works best at 0.7, I find, when making images from behind. Everything else works pretty well. Tanlines are kinda funky, I suppose.

This was all generated via Colab!

Anomalies:

  • Nothing that I'm too aware of. Hands are always weird, but I trained with higher reps this time compared to Kiara, so hopefully it gens better. Big ups to Kozue for the tip of higher reps regardless of dataset size.
